      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "Lucky drawers in the Occur\nd'Alene reservation lands are up\nin the air over a new ruling that\nhas just been made by the interior\ndepartment A telegram has been\nreceived by Register w. H. Batting\nof the United States land office,\nordering him to withdraw from the\nallotment 80 legal subdivisions of\nland. or about $500 acres in all."
